From: Peter Ujfalusi <peter.ujfalusi@ti.com>
Date: Tue, 1 Oct 2013 16:16:57 +0300
Subject: [PATCH 143/285] ARM: dts: am43x-epos-evm: McASP1 configuration

McASP1 is used for analog audio on the board, connected to tlv320aic3111
codec.

Signed-off-by: Peter Ujfalusi <peter.ujfalusi@ti.com>
Signed-off-by: Jyri Sarha <jsarha@ti.com>
Signed-off-by: Darren Etheridge <detheridge@ti.com>
[Kevin: The original patch taken from TI
ti-sdk-am437x-evm-07.01.00.00-Linux-x86-Install.bin]
Signed-off-by: Kevin Hao <kexin.hao@windriver.com>
---
 arch/arm/boot/dts/am43x-epos-evm.dts |   16 ++++++++++++++++
 1 files changed, 16 insertions(+), 0 deletions(-)

diff --git a/arch/arm/boot/dts/am43x-epos-evm.dts b/arch/arm/boot/dts/am43x-epos-evm.dts
index d36455a..cb2f104 100644
--- a/arch/arm/boot/dts/am43x-epos-evm.dts
+++ b/arch/arm/boot/dts/am43x-epos-evm.dts
@@ -626,3 +626,19 @@
 	pinctrl-names = "default";
 	pinctrl-0 = <&uart0_pins>;
 };
+
+&mcasp1 {
+	pinctrl-names = "default";
+	pinctrl-0 = <&mcasp1_pins>;
+
+	status = "okay";
+
+	op-mode = <0>;		/* MCASP_IIS_MODE */
+	tdm-slots = <2>;
+	/* 4 serializer */
+	serial-dir = <	/* 0: INACTIVE, 1: TX, 2: RX */
+		1 2 0 0
+	>;
+	tx-num-evt = <1>;
+	rx-num-evt = <1>;
+};
